<li>We are so sorry for your loss.  Your pet will be dearly missed.</li>
<li>With heartfelt sympathy, we extend our condolences on the passing of your beloved pet.</li>
<li>Holding you and your family close in our hearts.</li>
<li>May the love and memories of your pet bring you comfort.</li>
